# =============================================================================
# QUICK SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Generate or export your private key:
#    - From MetaMask: Settings > Security & Privacy > Show Private Keys
#    - Remove the '0x' prefix when adding to this file
#
# 3. Get Supabase credentials (optional, for pool data):
#    - Go to https://app.supabase.com
#    - Create/select your project
#    - Go to Settings > API
#    - Copy the Project URL and anon public key
#
# 4. Test the setup:
#    npm run futarchy-cli -- --help
